                        <interp inst="t18420509-name-366" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS FOWLER</persName>
                  </hi>. I paid the prisoner 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for the load of hay on the 1st of February.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I received the money from Mr. Fowler—I went to take a load of dung—I got drunk and lost the money. 
